    "This finely tuned focus promises to add value to both the scholarly community and policymakers grappling with the monumental challenge that COVID-19 represents.",
    "The pursuit of knowledge, especially in a field as dynamic and complex as the application of deep learning in healthcare, must be guided by well-articulated research questions or hypotheses.",
    "In this study, we pose pertinent questions and formulate hypotheses to guide the research process, focusing on understanding and enhancing the application of deep learning models for COVID-19 prediction in the UAE and Malaysia.",
